+                      <div class="cs-compare-step"><span class="cs-step-n">3</span>Send payment via your own bank</div>
+                      <div class="cs-compare-step"><span class="cs-step-n">4</span>Upload payment proof in the app</div>
+                      <div class="cs-compare-step"><span class="cs-step-n">5</span>Wait for seller to manually release funds</div>
