+            Completion rates more than doubled, deposit volumes grew meaningfully across our
+            key LatAm markets, and users who deposited via the new channel came back —
+            with over half showing repeated order and deposit behaviour. Fees were
+            competitive across the board, matching or beating the leading local players.
+          </p>
